This program is to experimentally verify that the Switching strategy works best for the Monty Hall Problem.

You can learn more about the problem here:
1. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Lb-6rxZxx0
2. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Monty_Hall_problem

This program illustrates that switching is indeed the best strategy, as described in the video.
Just doing it for fun! :D



